Consistency of judgements 

      Step 1 . Σ (原始的criteria pairwise matrix 
      
        *
      
      每個criteria所求得之相關權重) / 每個criteria所求得之相關權重
    





              c1
            

 
                
              

                a1
              

                a2
              

                a3
              

                Σ
              

                Div.
              



                a1
              


                  1*
                  
                    0.24
                  




                  2*
                  
                    0.14
                  




                  1/5*
                  
                    1
                  



                0.72
              

                /0.24=3
              



                a2
              


